---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = 'KokomaSoft TikTok Integration Privacy Policy | KokomaSoft';
const description = 'Privacy Policy for KokomaSoft features and services that integrate with TikTok developer products.';
---

<Layout
  lang="en"
  title={title}
  description={description}
  canonicalPath="/tiktok/privacy/"
  xDefaultPath="/tiktok/privacy/"
  ogType="article"
>
  <section class="legal-page">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow">KokomaSoft Legal</p>
      <h1>TikTok Integration Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="last-updated">Last updated: May 18, 2026</p>
      <p class="intro">
        This Privacy Policy explains how KokomaSoft handles information when our websites, mobile apps, or related services connect to or interact with TikTok developer products.
        It applies only to KokomaSoft-controlled services. TikTok's own services are governed by TikTok's policies.
      </p>

      <article class="legal-section">
        <h2>1. Information We May Process</h2>
        <p>
          Depending on the features you use and the permissions you grant, KokomaSoft may process account identifiers, profile information made available through TikTok authorization, content or media you choose to share, captions and metadata you provide, app usage events, device and browser information, error logs, and support messages.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="legal-section">
        <h2>2. How We Use Information</h2>
        <p>
          We use information to provide requested features, authenticate authorized connections, prepare or transmit content you choose to share, maintain service security, troubleshoot issues, respond to support requests, comply with legal obligations, and improve KokomaSoft services.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="legal-section">
        <h2>3. TikTok Authorization and Permissions</h2>
        <p>
          If a KokomaSoft feature asks you to authorize TikTok access, the permission screen will describe the access requested. We only use TikTok-related information for the feature you requested and in accordance with applicable TikTok developer requirements.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="legal-section">
        <h2>4. Sharing of Information</h2>
        <p>
          We do not sell personal information. We may share information with service providers that help operate KokomaSoft services, with TikTok when you request a TikTok-related action, when required by law, or when needed to protect users, KokomaSoft, TikTok, or the public from fraud, abuse, or security threats.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="legal-section">
        <h2>5. Data Retention and Deletion</h2>
        <p>
          We retain information only for as long as needed to provide the service, maintain security, resolve disputes, comply with legal obligations, or support legitimate business operations. You may request deletion of KokomaSoft-held information by contacting us at the email below.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="legal-section">
        <h2>6. Security</h2>
        <p>
          We use reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect information. No online service can guarantee perfect security, so you should avoid submitting sensitive information unless it is necessary for the feature you are using.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="legal-section">
        <h2>7. Children</h2>
        <p>
          KokomaSoft services are not directed to children. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children through TikTok-related features.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="legal-section">
        <h2>8. International Processing</h2>
        <p>
          KokomaSoft may process information in countries where we or our service providers operate. We take steps intended to handle information consistently with this policy and applicable legal requirements.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="legal-section">
        <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy to reflect changes in our services, TikTok developer requirements, legal obligations, or security practices. The updated policy will be posted on this page with a new last updated date.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="legal-section">
        <h2>10. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          For privacy questions or deletion requests, contact KokomaSoft at <a href="mailto:kokomasoft@gmail.com">kokomasoft@gmail.com</a>.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    padding: 5rem 0;
    background: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .legal-page .container {
    max-width: 820px;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 0.65rem;
  }

  h1 {
    color: var(--color-ink);
    font-size: clamp(2.1rem, 5vw, 3.4rem);
    line-height: 1.05;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .last-updated {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .intro,
  .legal-section p {
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.82;
  }

  .intro {
    margin-bottom: 2.25rem;
  }

  .legal-section {
    padding-top: 1.4rem;
    margin-top: 1.4rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .legal-section h2 {
    color: var(--color-ink);
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.65rem;
  }

  .legal-section a {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .legal-section a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
